name: ZippingIterator_hasNextTest
description: Unit tests for the hasNext method of the ZippingIterator class.

test_cases.name: testHasNextWithElements
test_cases.description: Tests the hasNext method when the ZippingIterator contains elements.

test_cases.name: testHasNextWithoutElements
test_cases.description: Tests the hasNext method when the ZippingIterator does not contain elements.

test_cases.name: testHasNextWithOneExhaustedIterator
test_cases.description: Tests the hasNext method when one of the iterators in the ZippingIterator is exhausted.

test_cases.name: testHasNextWithAllExhaustedIterators
test_cases.description: Tests the hasNext method when all iterators in the ZippingIterator are exhausted.

test_cases.name: testHasNextWithMultipleCalls
test_cases.description: Tests the hasNext method with multiple calls when the ZippingIterator contains elements.
